/*
 * SeeLink Installer Wizard
 * Compatible: Windows 7, 8, 10, 11 (x86 & x64)
 * Compiler:   MinGW-w64 or MSVC
 *
 * Build (MinGW):
 *   g++ -m32 -o SeeLinkSetup.exe seelink_installer.cpp -mwindows -lcomctl32 -lshell32 -lole32 -luuid -static
 *   (use -m64 for 64-bit, or build both and let the stub decide)
 *
 * The single-exe approach: compile as 32-bit. On a 64-bit OS the WOW64
 * layer runs it fine, and we detect the OS bitness at runtime to choose
 * the correct install paths (Program Files vs Program Files (x86)).
 */

